dcterms:description: A benchmark dataset designed to measure the effect of debiasing spurious correlations. The dataset consists of bird photographs from the CUB dataset combined with image backgrounds from the Places dataset. It has 4,795 training examples, 1,199 validation examples, and 5,794 testing examples. The task is to classify birds as waterbirds or landbirds while ignoring the background.
dcterms:title: Waterbirds dataset
